Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:36.20,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To evade the sudden alien attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:40.55,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the space battleship Macross\Nexecuted a hyperspace fold,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:45.52,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}catapulting the surrounding city, the island\Nand even some of the nearby ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:51.39,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}far into space, to arrive near\Nthe orbit of Pluto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:56.28,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The rescued civilians\Naboard the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.59,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}have recovered from\Ntheir initial shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.52,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}While unable to completely\Nshake free of their anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:06.32,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}the refugees slowly began to\Npick up the pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:09.15,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and the city has begun\Nto regain its balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:14.53,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(70,137)}TRANSFORMATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We waited in line all that time,\Nand this is what they give us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh!\NWelcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Minmay.\NShould you be out of bed so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:33.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sure.\NI'm fine now, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}By the way, where's Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I don't know.\NIsn't he still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}After all, he had to take care of\Nyou for more than a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I guess you're right.\NAnyway, Auntie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once we get things straightened up, are\Nwe going to reopen the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Reopen the restaurant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sure! \NI mean, look at everything we've salvaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:03:02.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, but the only food rations\Nthey gave us were these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, the restaurant stayed open\Nduring the Unification Wars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:14.29,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, the military did give us special\Nwartime ration status, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.82,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Besides, we're on a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:18.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you say you're reopening the restaurant,\NI'm sure they'll give you more rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Please, Uncle?\NAuntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, why not?\NWe can't keep loafin' around here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:33.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're right. Maybe re-opening the restaurant\Nwould be a nice way to keep ourselves busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Okay!\NWe'll be the first to give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Great!\NIt's settled, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll go get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Typical Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We'd better get busy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:46.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Careful, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:57.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\b1}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What are you up to?\N{\c&HFFFFFF&}Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:03.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, Mr. Mayor.\NWe're reopening the restaurant, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Reopening the restaurant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Are you serious?\NOn a battleship out at the edge of space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, come on, Mr. Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Even if we are far away from the Earth\Nand inside a spaceship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.29,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}this is still our town, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We should do things the\Nway we always have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Y'know, you're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?\NCheck it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, is this restaurant really open?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Welcome! As of today, the Nyan-Nyan\NChinese restaurant is open for business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:40.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm so happy! You soldiers are the first patrons\Nof our Chinese restaurant in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, we're honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Say, you're that Minmay girl\Neveryone's talking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They say you had\Nquite an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's right!\NIt was really rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I hear you were all alone with\Nsome guy for nearly two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, what did you two do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.83,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}"Do"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}C'mon, don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You know what we mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You really didn't do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, yeah. I hear the guy's stayin'\Nin a room upstairs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.94,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And...?\NWhat's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, you two fell for each other and\Nnow you're a couple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:18.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I swear, you're making me angry!\NIt's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}He's just a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now, are you going to order or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Right, right.\NI'll have some ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, ramen sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, I'll have ramen, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Okay, that's three orders of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just a friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\i1}"If we're going to die anyway,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.74,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\i1}"let's get it over with and throw\Nourselves out into space!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\i1}"Let's die together!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And the very next day,\NI'm "just a friend," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well? Does it look like we\Ncan use the main gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.05,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Please, take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is the main reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And this is the energy converter\Nfor the main gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:22.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They were initially connected to the\NFold System via energy conduits, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:27.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The connection was broken when the\Nfold system disappeared, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.95,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We don't have the resources to\Nrepair that amount of conduit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:37.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sir. We exploit the modular block\Nstructure of the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:43.16,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}In short, we replace this "block"\Nwith this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}However, the problem is that the\Nmain gun simply will not fire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}unless we first carry out\Nthis transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:55.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The ship will undergo structural changes\Ninternally and externally,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}causing major disruptions in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And, there's no other way\nto use the main gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:09.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Correct. I'm afraid that the\ntransformation is our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:16.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To throw the city into chaos again just as\Nwe're getting it quieted down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I just can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, there! We'd like two orders of\N{\i1}chashumen{\i0} and fried rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:48.94,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You little cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No matter what happens, you always\Nsurvive, just like a cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's just mean! Don't go putting me\Nin the same category as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, maybe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's with this scrap heap here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Scrap?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:30.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai, this racer was the second most\Nimportant thing to me, right after my own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And, you call it scrap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, it's wrecked and that's a fact.\NWhat's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What do you say Hikaru?\NYou up for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just look at that gloomy face of yours.\NIt's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.61,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai! Those fighters can\Nfly in space, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Uh-huh. The Valkyries have\Nthermo-nuclear reaction engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}With that much thrust, they can\Nfly just about anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How about it, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:56.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't you feel like trying to\Nfly one of those again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You mean join the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:04.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, it's pointless to just hang\Naround here and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:05.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is it, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:16.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Can a girl change in a single day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Can a girl be completely different today\Nfrom how she was yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You don't have to laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You've fallen for her, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}N...No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Relax, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:49.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Minmay was the one who said\Nyou were feeling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}and that I should come check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, cheer up and go on back\Nand show her you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The thing is, girls like her\Nare pretty fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Make sure you don't lose\Nher to another man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:09.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:23.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What? You have data on\Nthe alien homeworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, we were able to capture some images.\NPlease observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}These were taken by a reconnaissance Reguld.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Wh...What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, these aliens are miclones?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, sir. I also realized as much\Nupon viewing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:58.82,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There is an ancient legend in\nthe old Zentradi military records...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:03.83,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sir. It says, "Avoid the worlds\Nof the miclones."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:09.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Avoid the worlds of the miclones, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:15.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I believe we should not have any\Nfurther contact with this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:21.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Instead, we should concentrate on\Npursuing the target battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:24.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Understood. Fold at once\Nand initiate pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.78,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once we've de-folded, send a\Ndetachment of ships to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I want to probe\Ntheir capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, Hikaru.\NYou're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Uh, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.61,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's all right.\NCome in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, would you open the window for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:17.61,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Didn't I smash this when I\Nwas in the Battroid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.95,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:21.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's something I forgot and\Ndecided to go back for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You ended up saving me\Nwhile I was getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:33.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'll bet it's a letter from\Na boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:35.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No way!\NYou can read it if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This says you passed the preliminary\Nround for a singing audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.09,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:46.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, no wonder you sing so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Not that it matters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We're not on Earth anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}C'mon, don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:05.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}When we get back to Earth, you can\Nget another audition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\i1}If{\i0} we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Say, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I had one, but it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now, it's just scrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You mean your airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:34.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah.\NNow I don't have any dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.07,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A de-fold reaction has been\Ndetected at six o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We have a report from the radar room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Unidentified objects have appeared\Nbehind us and are closing fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Enemy ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hayase!\NTake us to battle stations, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:05.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.82,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Enemy attack!\NEnemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Valkyrie squadrons, all units, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.94,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I repeat, Valkyrie squadrons,\Nall units, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Wow!\NThe town looks so nice, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:40.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.39,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Air-raid alert!\NAir-raid alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Will we be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Relax. Sempai and the others\Nwill take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's always "Sempai, Sempai"\Nwith you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're as good a pilot\Nas he is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Dammit! They're a lot more slippery\Nhere than they were on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is gonna take some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our lead detachment has moved\Ninto firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Strange.\NThey're not firing their main gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Damned miclones.\NWhat are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:35.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Why not provoke them a little more\Nand see how they react?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:37.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes.\NThat is acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Authorize the lead detachment to open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Enough to get the enemy\Nship to return fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The enemy ships are firing on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A section of the sub-control\Nsystems has been damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}However, it looks like we'll be\Nable to manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.91,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:33.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We've lost auxiliary\Ngun turrets Numbers 2 and 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:39.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Immediate repair is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Section 4 has been\Nheavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sub-control systems report heavy damage\Nand several casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's it! Send a message to all sections:\NPrepare to fire the main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:58.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We're going to initiate\Nthe ship-wide transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, if we do that, the city will be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Th...That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just do it!\NWe don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Attention all sections!\NAttention all sections!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Take positions for firing\Nthe main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.96,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation will commence\Nin three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:26.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?\NDid she say transformation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No way!\NThat's just nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.47,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}T-minus two minutes, thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.91,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Attention all civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:37.41,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our ship is to make a\Ntransformation in 60 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.34,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.65,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}For your safety, please hold tightly\Nonto anything within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I bet Mr. Focker and the others\Nare in battle right now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Are you saying, I should join the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's not exactly what I mean, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}...well, airplanes are your dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:02.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, if I join the military, you and I won't\Nget to see each other very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't be silly!\NWe're on the same ship, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.41,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And, we can see each other\Nwhenever you have time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If I survive, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:14.23,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But, it's the same for all the soldiers\Nwho come to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:15.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}All the same, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:18.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}To you, I guess I'm no different\Nfrom any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}T-minus ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Problems in any of the sections?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}G block and D block are a little\Nbehind, but they should be able to manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:29.76,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}T-minus five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:34.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Initiate ship-wide transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}J, K and L blocks, initiate transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Please increase output to the No. 7 reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation is underway in section 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.84,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}There's insufficient power in J block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.07,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ship-wide transformation is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:52.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maybe I'd be happier if the city\Nand everything else
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}was blasted to space dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What?! How can you say\Nsomething so selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.06,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Fine by me!\NMe too, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:17.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.02,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Three minutes have elapsed since the\Norder to begin transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.35,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Reconfiguration is now 11.5% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:40.92,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:54.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation of the starboard\Nsection is 75% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:58.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation of the port\Nsection is 80% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Main gun system is nominal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, that's the Macross's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}...transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Transformation is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The enemy ships have launched 40 or 50\Nsmaller units, closing rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Never mind them!\NFire the main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:37.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Wh...What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The enemy ships have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:23.82,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We did it!\NThank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:31.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Get me a ship-wide damage report at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:33.61,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Attention all civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:37.95,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Our sincerest apologies, but\Nthanks to your cooperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:42.16,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}we were able to fire the main gun\Nand destroy the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:45.86,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If you were injured or your\Nhome was damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:49.16,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}please inform your nearest branch office\Nor police substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:53.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, you said you wanted\Nthe city to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:57.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, but... I didn't think that\Nsomething like THIS would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:00.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I wonder if the restaurant was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm going to do it, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:03.30,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:05.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm going to join the military!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:06.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:11.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I can't just keep standing around\Ndoing nothing, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:22.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Valkyrie squadrons, return to base!
